{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378330/extras/library_logo_RekindledTrails_elonogated.png?t=1740131663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>A light beckons you forward\u2026 Will you sell your soul?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In Rekindled Trails you are enlisted by a being of flame to reignite the world of Aurteris! With the creature safely in your lantern, set out on a journey of magical exploration, chilling nights and odd encounters.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378330/extras/SteampageSubTitle01.png?t=1740131663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378330/extras/Gameplay_BoneWalking_Steam.gif?t=1740131663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On your journey you will explore a new world, which is as beautiful as it is mysterious. Light your path with the help of magical lanterns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378330/extras/SteampageSubTitle06.png?t=1740131663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378330/extras/Gameplay_SortingItems_Steam.gif?t=1740131663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fish, pull and mine natural resources, stuffing your scrapbook full with information!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3378330/extras/SteampageSubTitle02.png?t=1740131663\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph